1. Fix error after create project
	+ Structure:
		src
			main
				java(src/main/java)				--> Backend: code and configuration(config by java)
				resources(src/main/resources)	--> Backend: code and resources(.xml, .properties)
				webapp							--> Frontend: code
					WEB-INF(configure)
						web.xml(main-config with xml)
					index.jsp(first come when start application)
	+ index.jsp(error first)
	--> The default superclass, "javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet", according to the project's Dynamic Web Module facet version (2.3), was 
 not found on the Java Build Path.
 	--> java extends/implement HttpServlet
 		--> import dependency for servlet/jsp(contains HttpServlet)


